      <p
        class="mt-4 text-lg sm:text-2xl text-center mb-32 sm:mb-24 max-w-[90%] sm:max-w-[45%] mx-auto leading-[1.45rem]"
      >
        Utiliza la siguiente lista para hacer un <span
          class="text-[#6610F2] text-bold">ejercicio de discriminación</span
        > de las <span class="text-bold"
          >letras <span class="text-[#6610F2]">s</span> y <span
            class="text-[#6610F2]">z</span
          >:
        </span>
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex w-full justify-center z-10 transform -translate-y-24 sm:translate-y-0 relative"
      >
        <TeacherMessage client:load />
      </div>

      <img
        src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Superior_xl.svg"
        alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Superior"
        class="w-3/4 hidden justify-center mx-auto transform -translate-y-12 sm:block"
      />
      <div
        class="relative w-full max-w-[350px] sm:max-w-[650px] mx-auto py-32 sm:py-16"
      >
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Superior.svg"
          alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Superior"
          class="w-full transform -translate-y-56 sm:hidden -z-10"
        />

        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="w-full px-24 transform translate-y-20 sm:translate-y-32">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 gap-x-32 sm:gap-x-0">
              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zoom
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zoom.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Seven
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Seven.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zone
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zone.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Sister
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Sister.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Zebra
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Zebra.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-8">
                <p class="text-[#6610F2] text-3xl sm:text-5xl text-extrabold">
                  Sorry
                </p>
                <AudioPlayer
                  audio_path={"/audio/z/Sorry.mp3"}
                  className="w-24 h-24 sm:w-20 sm:h-20"
                  client:load
                />
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Inferior.svg"
          alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Inferior"
          class="w-full transform translate-y-48 sm:translate-y-28 -z-10 absolute sm:hidden"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <img
          src="/images/svg/global/Contenedor_Audios_Inferior_xl.svg"
          alt="Contenedor de Audios Parte Inferior"
          class="w-3/4 lg:w-1/2 hidden mx-auto transform -z-10 absolute translate-y-64 sm:block"
        />
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- Seccion de "Como podemos pronunciar el fonema" -->
    <section class="-mb-32 c400:-mb-44 xl:-mb-48 overflow-hidden">
      <p
        class="mt-4 text-xl sm:text-3xl text-bold text-center mb-12 sm:mb-20 max-w-[62%] mx-auto leading-[1.45rem]"
      >
        ¿Cómo podemos<span class="text-[#6610F2]"> pronunciar z</span>
        en inglés?
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-[15px] w-[85%] sm:w-[75%] mx-auto">
        <div
          class="col-start-1 col-span-11 -mb-16 max-w-[97%] sm:col-start-1 sm:col-span-7 sm:mb-16 sm:max-w-[90%] xl:col-span-8 xl:mb-8"
        >
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-2xl text-left leading-[1.45rem]">
            Comienza <span class="text-bold"
              >pronunciando la letra <span class="text-[#6610F2]">s</span> en castellano</span
            >. Luego, mientras pronuncias la <span class="text-bold"
              >letra <span class="text-[#6610F2]">s</span></span
            >, pon dos dedos sobre tu garganta e
            <span class="text-bold">imita el zumbido de una abeja</span>.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div
          class="col-start-7 col-span-5 sm:col-start-8 sm:col-span-4 flexjustify-center items-center -mb-8 sm:-mb-48"
        >
          <img
            src="/images/png/z/Abeja.png"
            alt="Abeja"
            class="w-32 h-40 sm:w-48 sm:h-48 transform sm:rotate-[25.53deg] rotate-[25.53deg] -translate-y-6 c500:translate-x-28 sm:-translate-y-2 lg:-translate-y-2 xl:-translate-y-48 translate-x-16 c400:translate-x-20 sm:translate-x-4"
          />
        </div>

        <div
          class="col-end-13 col-span-12 ml-auto sm:col-end-13 sm:col-span-8 transform -translate-y-8 sm:translate-y-4"
        >
          <p class="text-lg sm:text-2xl text-right leading-[1.45rem]">
            <span class="text-bold">Si te vibra la garganta, estás</span>
            <span class="block xs:inline c400:block sm:inline"
              ><span class="text-bold"
                >pronunciando la letra <span class="text-[#6610F2]"> z</span
                ></span
              >; si no vibra</span
            >
            <span class="inline xs:inline c400:block sm:inline"
              >como el zumbido de una abeja,</span
            >
            <span class="block xs:inline c400:block c550:inline sm:inline">
              estás pronunciando la letra <span class="text-bold text-[#6610F2]">s</span
              >.</span
            >
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-start-1 col-span-7 flex justify-center items-center">
          <img
            src="/images/png/z/Voiced.png"
            alt="Abeja"
            class="w-48 h-48 sm:w-72 sm:h-72 transform -translate-y-20 -translate-x-12 c400:-translate-y-36
                                                              c500:-translate-y-52 c550:-translate-x-20 sm:-translate-y-48 sm:-translate-x-24"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="mt-10">
      <div class="lg:max-w-4xl sm:max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 sm:gap-x-12 mb-14">
          <div>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-4">
              <video
                src="/videos/z/Muestra_Vibracion_S.mp4"
                controls
